==DVD release==
On January 15, 2013, [[DreamWorks Classics]] released ''The Jackson 5ive: The Complete Animated Series'' on DVD and [[Blu-ray Disc|Blu-ray]] in Region 1 for the very first time.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tvshowsondvd.com/news/Jackson-5ive-The-Complete-Animated-Series/17658|title=The Jackson 5ive DVD news: Announcement for The Jackson 5ive - The Completed Animated Series - TVShowsOnDVD.com|website=Tvshowsondvd.com|accessdate=26 November 2017|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171116133859/http://www.tvshowsondvd.com/news/Jackson-5ive-The-Complete-Animated-Series/17658|archivedate=16 November 2017|df=}}</ref>  The 2-disc set features all 23 episodes of the series. For the remastered print (''The Jackson 5ive: The Complete Animated Series''), the mono soundtrack was replaced by the 5.1 surround soundtrack in the songs, the rest of the scenes kept the mono soundtrack. As of 2018, both the Blu-ray and the DVD are now out of print and very hard to find.

